Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.78,0:05:04.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uzume.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.04,0:05:21.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The smell of blood is dyed into your skin.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.05,0:05:24.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You certainly are a demon.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.93,0:05:37.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will use your power as much as I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.30,0:05:43.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must kill all those who disturb me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.45,0:07:04.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uzume...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.60,0:07:06.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,what are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.33,0:07:12.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go back to the mansion.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.65,0:07:18.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uzume, can't you hear what I'm saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.30,0:07:22.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do as I please.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.60,0:07:30.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You see... I won't take orders from you anymore, Gisuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.68,0:07:58.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Uzume...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.69,0:08:01.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Please take care of Uzume.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.98,0:08:43.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm, why did you summon me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.71,0:08:46.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't talk to you if you're out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.32,0:08:47.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.61,0:08:48.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.00,0:09:03.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have something to ask you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.14,0:09:05.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To ask me, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.67,0:09:08.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chen was killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.72,0:09:11.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-So, what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.73,0:09:13.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't order it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.18,0:09:19.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-Take a look at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.24,0:09:25.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I ordered Aoi to do just what is written here, as usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.95,0:09:35.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did you get this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.26,0:09:38.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The usual hiding place, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.97,0:09:41.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't write it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.71,0:09:44.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.45,0:09:47.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With Chen's death,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.44,0:09:51.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the colossal wealth from the opium trade will disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.80,0:09:57.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How are you going to make up for this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.17,0:10:13.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.14,0:11:08.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Karyuu-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.53,0:11:11.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Magoroku?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.71,0:11:19.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, stay right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.72,0:11:24.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to listen to something.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.75,0:11:54.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A trap?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.67,0:11:57.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.73,0:12:01.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That order was a fake.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.49,0:12:04.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And because of that, I'm in real trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.94,0:12:12.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The truth is, the jobs that I asked Aoi to do were mostly{\fscx200}-
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.14,0:12:17.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it could be that all of them were orders from that man.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.16,0:12:20.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That man?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.45,0:12:26.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The man who was with the foreigner you killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.05,0:12:42.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.56,0:12:48.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A terrifying man called "Black Jyuuzou."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.73,0:12:53.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He believes that the ends justify the means.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.41,0:12:54.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If anyone obstructs him,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.96,0:12:58.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,even if it's one of his own men, he will kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.34,0:13:03.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, he is the boss of all assassins,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.18,0:13:06.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,feared by both the Bakufu and the Imperial Court.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.18,0:13:06.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fnBorzoiBold\fs20\3c&000000&}[Note: The Bakufu were the bureaucracy of the Tokugawa Shogunate.]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.26,0:13:10.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There isn't a murder he hasn't been involved in.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.33,0:13:13.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, Karyuu-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.94,0:13:19.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,don't you know him better than you know me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.68,0:13:24.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A long time ago, when you were still a child,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.11,0:13:28.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,your house was burned down,\N and your entire family was murdered.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.28,0:13:32.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That man was responsible, wasn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.50,0:13:33.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Magoroku!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.49,0:13:35.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.67,0:13:39.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just telling you what I've heard.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.53,0:13:44.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, it's a cruel story.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.05,0:13:49.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were getting orders to kill from your enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.89,0:13:52.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is he now?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.04,0:13:57.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First, I'll tell you something else that's interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.85,0:13:59.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.28,0:14:01.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is another secret about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.98,0:14:03.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Another secret?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.40,0:14:07.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then again, it might be better if you didn't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.83,0:14:18.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Magoroku!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.92,0:14:21.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, but I have to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.99,0:14:26.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's hiding in that foreigner's ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.03,0:14:32.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one can reach him while he's there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.26,0:14:36.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was just for a short time,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.53,0:14:39.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but it was nice to see you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.59,0:14:44.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This will be our last meeting, so take care.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.76,0:14:47.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! Magoroku!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.53,0:15:03.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Karyuu, that bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.28,0:15:07.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Never let her escape, do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.51,0:15:11.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chase her to the ends of the earth and kill her!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.84,0:15:12.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.72,0:16:43.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have great skill.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.55,0:16:47.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Truly, you've grown to be an adept shinobi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.32,0:16:50.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I really should have killed you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.98,0:17:06.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this supposed to be revenge?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.56,0:17:14.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't become that weak yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.56,0:17:23.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Surely, this is a blood feud.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.89,0:17:26.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your strength reminds me of your father.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.73,0:17:27.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.40,0:17:32.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Karyuu. Don't you want to know why your house was attacked?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.35,0:17:41.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm... Your father was the chief of the Bakufu's secret service.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.67,0:17:45.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was our biggest enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.11,0:17:47.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that why you killed him?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.73,0:18:19.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you looking at me like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.22,0:18:22.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know that in a world of peace,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.24,0:18:26.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we shinobi will be treated like scum.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.83,0:18:30.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I started this business.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.21,0:18:32.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was to survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.88,0:18:34.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.72,0:18:48.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tell you something interesting, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.17,0:18:54.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't the only one your father was after.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.99,0:18:57.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was also pursuing Aoi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.33,0:19:16.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You may not know this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.42,0:19:21.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aoi abducted children from the families she killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.39,0:19:23.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then she raised them as shinobi,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.99,0:19:28.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and let them work under her after they grew up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.21,0:19:31.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.88,0:19:33.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She chose them with great care.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.94,0:19:38.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In all likelihood, a child like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.07,0:20:13.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.24,0:20:19.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Were you...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.25,0:20:21.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,with that man?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.33,0:20:28.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I went easy on you before...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.87,0:20:32.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but that will never happen again!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.72,0:21:14.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.90,0:21:17.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.24,0:21:20.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you hate me so much?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.74,0:21:24.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Karyuu.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.90,0:21:28.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you remember that girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.01,0:21:29.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.56,0:21:34.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's the girl you took pity on and spared that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.09,0:22:11.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.61,0:22:28.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's your fault that I am what I am now.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.43,0:22:33.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.33,0:22:48.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Blood. Blood!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.79,0:22:59.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you with that man?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.75,0:23:02.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's because he told me everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.69,0:23:03.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.94,0:23:07.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That you were the shinobi from that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.40,0:23:10.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, I lured you out here.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.25,0:23:13.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You entrapped Magoroku!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.07,0:23:16.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, to make this place your grave.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.18,0:23:37.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.11,0:23:40.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Blood? Blood?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.73,0:23:43.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That much of my blood from...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.05,0:23:54.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Karyuu!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.99,0:24:00.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up, Karyuu!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.51,0:24:26.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uzume!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.01,0:24:32.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gisuke...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.87,0:24:37.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because of this... everything is...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.52,0:24:43.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.41,0:25:49.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Both Uzume's father and I...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.55,0:25:53.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,were originally from the same group of shinobi.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.49,0:25:57.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uzume's father realized that there was a peaceful world out there,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.87,0:26:00.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so he gave up the way of the shinobi,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.37,0:26:04.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and chose to live as a merchant with the rest of his clan.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.61,0:26:10.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that man, Black Jyuuzou, wouldn't let us leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.16,0:26:13.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Before anyone noticed that Uzume's father was happy,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.30,0:26:16.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jyuuzou ordered the surviving shinobi...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.36,0:26:19.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to assassinate him.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.00,0:26:30.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was told not to let Uzume follow the way of the shinobi.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.55,0:26:33.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.48,0:26:39.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I ended up being the instrument of Uzume's death.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.29,0:26:49.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From the time she was a child, if Uzume ever saw blood,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.08,0:26:52.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there was nothing to be done with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.49,0:26:58.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So in any case, the consequences would have been the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.25,0:27:01.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.96,0:27:04.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.27,0:27:08.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I hadn't killed Uzume's father...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.45,0:27:14.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, Uzume was the same as me.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.11,0:27:20.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I made her take up the same destiny as I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.98,0:27:28.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, forgive me...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.94,0:27:43.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.57,0:27:51.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.29,0:28:02.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Karyuu, the world is going to change tremendously.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.81,0:28:07.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It will not be a world for samurai anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.29,0:28:18.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.79,0:28:22.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kikka.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.67,0:28:31.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You two were very unkind to leave me behind!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.81,0:28:33.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.90,0:28:35.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think that
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.73,0:28:39.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it's boring without Karyuu-sama around,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.74,0:28:42.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I've decided to go with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.74,0:28:44.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.53,0:28:48.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told my family that I'll be traveling for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.16,0:28:49.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.44,0:28:52.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're together again.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.17,0:28:55.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. We're inseparable!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.95,0:28:59.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey. What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.17,0:29:01.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.15,0:29:03.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop that!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.22,0:29:20.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.80,0:29:23.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't leave me!
